{% raw %}
<style>
  :root{--ink-3:#4d4d4d}
  body{font-size:var(--fs-body)}

  .lp{max-width:680px;padding:40px 0 8px}
  @media(min-width:760px){.lp{padding:58px 0 12px}}
  .lp .eyebrow{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:var(--fs-label);letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--green-d);font-weight:700}
  .lp h1{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:var(--fs-display);line-height:1.04;letter-spacing:-.025em;margin:14px 0 0;color:var(--ink);max-width:20ch}
  .lp .thesis{font-size:var(--fs-body);color:var(--ink-2);margin:18px 0 0;line-height:1.5;max-width:52ch}

  .signup{margin:28px 0 0;max-width:480px}
  .signup form{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .signup input[type=email]{flex:1;min-width:220px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:var(--fs-small);padding:14px 15px;border:1.5px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;background:#fff;color:var(--ink)}
  .signup input[type=email]:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--green)}
  .signup button{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:var(--fs-label);letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;color:#fff;background:var(--green);border:none;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 24px;cursor:pointer}
  .signup button:hover{background:var(--green-d)}
  .signup .fine{font-size:var(--fs-small);color:var(--ink-2);margin-top:13px;line-height:1.55}

  .inside{max-width:680px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);margin:42px 0 0;padding:24px 0 4px}
  .inside h2{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:var(--fs-h2);color:var(--ink);margin:0 0 6px}
  .inside .intro{font-size:var(--fs-small);line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-2);max-width:62ch}
  .issueparts{margin-top:18px;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
  .issuepart{display:grid;grid-template-columns:112px 1fr;gap:20px;padding:15px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);align-items:baseline}
  .issuepart .k{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:var(--fs-label);letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--green-d);font-weight:600}
  .issuepart p{font-size:var(--fs-small);line-height:1.5;color:var(--ink-2)}
  .madefor{font-size:var(--fs-small);line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink-2);margin-top:20px;max-width:60ch}
  .madefor a{color:var(--green);font-weight:500}
  @media(max-width:520px){
    .signup form{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .signup input[type=email]{min-width:0;width:100%}
    .signup button{width:100%;min-height:48px}
    .issuepart{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:4px}
  }
</style>

<div class="wrap">
  <section class="lp">
    <span class="eyebrow">The weekly email</span>
    <h1>Mexico, once a week.</h1>
    <p class="thesis">Once a week, I send the few things that changed in Mexico's economy, politics, and relationship with the US that I think are worth knowing. The numbers come from original sources. The links are included if you want to go deeper.</p>

    <!-- Our own form -> /api/subscribe (Cloudflare function -> beehiiv, key server-side). No third-party UI. -->
    <div class="signup">
      <form class="subform" method="post" action="/api/subscribe" novalidate>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="you@email.com" aria-label="Email address" autocomplete="email" inputmode="email" required />
        <label class="hp-field" aria-hidden="true">Website<input type="text" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" /></label>
        <button type="submit">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
      <div class="fine submsg" aria-live="polite">One email a week. Unsubscribe whenever you want.</div>
      <div class="privacy-note">Your email is handled by Beehiiv for this newsletter. <a href="/privacy.html">Privacy</a>.</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="inside" aria-labelledby="inside-title">
    <h2 id="inside-title">What's in it</h2>
    <p class="intro">Each issue starts with the biggest development of the week, then the numbers that moved and the context that helped me understand them.</p>
    <div class="issueparts">
      <div class="issuepart"><span class="k">The week</span><p>The developments I would want someone to tell me about.</p></div>
      <div class="issuepart"><span class="k">The numbers</span><p>The current value, what changed, the period it covers, and the original source.</p></div>
      <div class="issuepart"><span class="k">My read</span><p>What I think it means, clearly labeled. You are welcome to ignore that part.</p></div>
      <div class="issuepart"><span class="k">Next</span><p>The releases, votes, and decisions coming up.</p></div>
    </div>
    <p class="madefor">I made the email for the same reason I made the site. I was tired of opening ten tabs and still not knowing what had actually changed. This is the recap I wanted once a week. Written by <a href="/about.html">Alan Lacroix</a>.</p>
  </section>
</div>
{% endraw %}
